These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, water, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the person drinking water is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person drinking water##6
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | tea  | lemonade | water | coffee  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
House: victorian, craftsman, modern, cape-cod
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
3. the victorian house is the journalist##1
4. the cape-cod house is between the victorian house and the craftsman house##2
5. the craftsman house is somewhere between the modern house and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| House   | modern | craftsman          | cape-cod | victorian     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, lemonade, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | tea | lemonade     | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

