2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the futuristic house##1
4. the craftsman house is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the cottage house is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the cottage house is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| House   | farmhouse   | futuristic         | craftsman   | cottage    |
| Sport         | parkour | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse |

