.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, iced-tea, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, indie, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
6. the person drinking water is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
7. the person drinking water is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage          | water | hot-chocolate | juice  | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | pop         | indie | ambient |

