.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, drama, disaster, superhero
1. the person watching drama movies is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person watching disaster movies##7
3. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
4. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
5. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola      | sprite | almond-milk | water   |
| Movie-Genre      | martial-arts | disaster | superhero  | drama |

