.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker, entrepreneur, project-manager
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, davidoff, swisher, vegafina
1. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the vegafina-smoker##8
2. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the right of the swisher-smoker##5
3. the dressmaker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
4. the swisher-smoker is somewhere between the davidoff-smoker and the dressmaker##7
5. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the project-manager##8
6. the project-manager is somewhere between the davidoff-smoker and the entrepreneur##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Job     | dressmaker | entrepreneur | project-manager | doctor     |
| Cigar   | dunhill   | swisher        | vegafina          | davidoff |

