.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, indie, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, argentine, dutch, american
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of pop and the malaysian##2
2. the american is on the far left##1
3. the american is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the malaysian##5
5. the argentine is the argentine##1
6. the fan of indie is not the dutch##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the malaysian is not to the left of the argentine##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | classical | indie | dubstep |
| Nationality     | american | argentine       | malaysian  | dutch    |

