.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-10::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, whist, backgammon, scrabble
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person playing scrabble is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the snowmobile##2
2. the person driving the airplane is not the person playing whist##6
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8
5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Game         | backgammon | monopoly      | scrabble   | whist  |
| Transport   | taxi    | motorbike | airplane | snowmobile |

