3. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
4. the person who growslily is not to the right of the japanese##8
5. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the left of the indian##8
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Nationality   | dutch     | japanese | indian | german |
