.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
City: liverpool, boston, london, san-francisco
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, filmmaking, puzzles, reading
1. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##8
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the person traveling to boston##8
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to london is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
6. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
7. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| City    | boston        | san-francisco | london      | liverpool    |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | filmmaking | reading |

