.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, salsa, country, classical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, ice-hockey, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the fan of pop##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of pop is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of classical is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the fan of salsa##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
8. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | classical | salsa         | country    | pop       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

