.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, electrician, doctor, freelancer
 1. the freelancer is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the doctor##1
 4. the doctor is not to the right of the electrician##8
 5. the freelancer is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the electrician is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the doctor##8
 9. the electrician is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the accountant##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Job   | accountant | freelancer  | doctor     | electrician    |

