2. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person who likes ivory##8
3. the person who likes ivory is the person who likes ivory##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person eating avocado is between the person who likes ivory and the person eating peas##2
7. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | peas        | avocado | asparagus | grapefruit |
| Color   | aquamarine | purple | ivory   | blue    |

