1. the fan of pop is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
2. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the fan of punk##8
3. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the fan of punk and the fan of pop##7
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5
5. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
6. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
7. the fan of jazz is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | disco  | pop | jazz  | punk  |
| Transport   | bike | car   | trike | jet-ski |

